@startuml sequence_dashboard
!theme plain
title Dashboard Layout: Add / Move / Resize / Persist

actor User
participant "DashboardPage" as P
participant "DashboardsController" as C
participant "Handler" as H
database "DB" as DB

User -> P: open /dashboard
P -> C: GET /api/dashboards/me
C -> H: GetMyDashboardQuery
H -> DB: SELECT DashboardLayout WHERE UserId=...
H --> C: { json }
C --> P: 200
P --> User: render gridster

User -> P: add widget / drag / resize
P -> P: update local state
P -> C: PUT /api/dashboards/me {json} (debounced 300ms)
C -> H: SaveDashboardCommand
H -> DB: UPSERT layout
H --> C: ok
C --> P: 200
@enduml
